title: Episode 140 | "On A Different Time"
description: On this weeks episode, Joe, Rory, and Mal address how the internet got finessed by Keaton Jones and his family (19:42). Also, we know what “the streets” are saying, but is Big Sean’s new project really trash? The guys get into a heated debate over Sean’s new project (1:05:40). Plus the guys discuss if being nominated for an academy award still matter these days (1:24:00). Other topics include: -Joe thinks he has the scoop on something (41:30) -Jeezy’s song with J.Cole and Kendrick Lamar (1:47:20) -Sports segment (1:31:53) Sleeper Picks of the Week: Mal: SoulGroupUniverse “Brainstorm” | https://youtu.be/0taWa3RadNo Rory: Mone Corleone “Rising” | https://youtu.be/BJ1n2_j-ap8 Joe: Jazmine Sullivan “Forever Don’t Last” | https://youtu.be/7caf6ouyPFo
